<plot>This news documentary program provided an in-depth look at stories and issues that the regular news programs could only give a brief glimpse of. Hosted primarily by Bob Young, this show tackled such issues as the assassination of President Kennedy, the civil rights movement, and the cold war, before being cancelled in 1964.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?019813</url></doc>
